jcr:content.jcr:title: Blast from the Past Camporee hosted by Community 4

data.details:
Blast from the Past Community 4 Camporee

Join us for a fun-filled weekend as we explore different decades including the Roaring 20’s, Rosie the River’s 40’s, Psychedelic Tie-Dye 70’s & much more!!  Be sure you’re not “Chopped” from the SWAPs Challenge and wear your best poodle skirt or 50’s attire for the Saturday night Sock Hop!  Fee includes a Camp Souvenir T-Shirt & Patch.

** Camporees are open to all registered Girl Scouts of Gateway Council.  All adults must be registered and approved volunteers.  Safety Activity Checkpoints girl to adult ratios must be met to attend this event.

** Last day to register: November 27, 2015
